    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><note>Il principe Arechi II offre al monastero di S. Sofia di Benevento (prosegue
                        l'elenco iniziato con il doc. 3535):</note></ab> <ab>(…) [8] Seu et <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3405"><rs key="#Churches">ęcclesia</rs> Sancti
                            Martini</orgName> que posita est in <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/3408">Motola</placeName> in nostro <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Mention #Residential"
                            >territorio</rs>, ubi <name ref="Maurus">Maurus</name>
                        <rs key="#Prevosts #rectorOf">presbyter</rs> sedere videtur, cum omnibus
                        sibi pertinentibus sicut ipse presbyter <rs key="#Cartula">per suam
                            cartulam</rs> omnem conquestum suum <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/85"
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Churches #Monasteries">Sancte Sophie <rs
                                key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs></orgName> tradedit. Similiter et
                        substantia <name ref="Aurimo">Auremoni</name> quam sub nostri <rs
                            key="#Palatium">palatii</rs>
                        <rs key="#Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium">mundio</rs> in predicti Sancti Martini
                            <rs key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs> tradedit, nostra vero potestas omnia
                        hec in Sancte Sophie monasterio firmabimus possidendum, et concessimus
                        nominato monasterio Sancte Sophie ex ipso <geogName
                            key="#Gai #Fiscal_property #Mention #Residential" ref="#estates/3403"
                                ><rs key="#Gai">gaio</rs> Motola</geogName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >territorium</rs> miliaria novem. (…)</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
